title: Re: Hillary Clinton trolls Donald Trump over 3-0 appeals court decision, but numbers aren’t her friends
text:
Hillary Clinton trolls Donald Trump over 3-0 appeals court decision, but numbers aren’t her friends Posted at 7:54 pm   Brett T. 
The only thing less surprising than the liberal 9th Circuit Court of Appeals upholding the stay on President Trump’s travel ban is that the president quickly responded on Twitter, in all caps, nonetheless. SEE YOU IN COURT, THE SECURITY OF OUR NATION IS AT STAKE! 
— Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) February 9, 2017 
In this case though, the office of Washington state Attorney General Bob Ferguson beat the president to the punch, issuing its own all-caps victory cry. DENIED. UNANIMOUS. PER CURIUM. 
— WA Attorney General (@AGOWA) February 9, 2017 @AGOWA excellent usage of spacing, all caps, and periods. 10/10 subtweet.
